Handsome Katydid Distribution in the Carolinas

This is the Handsome Meadow Katydid Orchelimum pulchellum

DISMO Occurance Maps

Katy_dismo <- gbif("orchelimum", species = "pulchellum", ext = c(-85,-75,34,37),
                   geo = TRUE, sp = TRUE, download = TRUE,
                   removeZeros = TRUE)
## 90 records found
## 0-90 records downloaded
Katy_dismo_df <- cbind.data.frame(Katy_dismo@coords[,1],
                                  Katy_dismo@coords[,2])

colnames(Katy_dismo_df) <- c("x","y")

View(Katy_dismo_df)
us <- map_data("state")

ggplot(data = Katy_dismo_df, aes(x=x, y=y)) +
  geom_polygon(data = us, aes(x=long, y = lat, group = group),
               fill = "white", color="black") +
  geom_point() + xlab("Longitude") + ylab("Latitude") +
  coord_fixed(xlim = c(-85,-75), ylim = c(34,37)) +
  xlab("Longitude") + ylab("Latitude") + ggtitle("Handsome Katydid Occurance in the Carolinas") + 
  theme_bw() + theme(plot.title = element_text(hjust = 0.5)) + 
  theme(panel.grid.major = element_blank(), 
        panel.grid.minor = element_blank(),
        panel.background = element_rect(fill = "lightblue"))

RGBIF Data Map

Katy_rgbif <- occ_data(scientificName = "Orchelimum pulchellum",
                       hasCoordinate = TRUE, limit = 200,
                       decimalLongitude = "-85, -75", 
                       decimalLatitude = "34, 37")


Katy_rgbif_df <- cbind.data.frame(Katy_rgbif$data$scientificName,
                                   Katy_rgbif$data$decimalLatitude,
                                   Katy_rgbif$data$decimalLongitude,
                                   Katy_rgbif$data$year,
                                  Katy_rgbif$data$stateProvince)

colnames(Katy_rgbif_df) <- c("species","y","x","year", "state")

Katy_rgbif_df <- Katy_rgbif_df[complete.cases(Katy_rgbif_df[1:4]),]

us <- map_data("state")

ggplot() +
  geom_polygon(data = us, aes(x=long, y = lat, group = group),
               fill = "white", color="black") +
  geom_point(data = Katy_rgbif_df, aes(x=x, y=y, color = species), size = 3) +
  coord_fixed(xlim = c(-85,-75), ylim = c(33,37)) +
  xlab("Longitude") + ylab("Latitude") + ggtitle("Handsome Katydid in the Carolinas") + 
  guides(color=guide_legend("Legend", override.aes = list(size = 4))) +
  theme_bw() + theme(plot.title = element_text(hjust = 0.5)) + 
  theme(legend.position = "bottom") +
  theme(legend.title.align = 0.5, legend.box.just = "center") +
  theme(panel.grid.major = element_blank(), 
        panel.grid.minor = element_blank(),
        panel.background = element_rect(fill = "lightblue"))

colors <- colorFactor(c("#F8766D","#00BA38","#619CFF"), Katy_rgbif_df$state)

leaflet(Katy_rgbif_df) %>% 
  addTiles() %>% 
  addCircleMarkers(Katy_rgbif_df$x,
                   Katy_rgbif_df$y,
                   popup = Katy_rgbif_df$species,
                   weight = 2,
                   color = colors(Katy_rgbif_df$state),
                   fillOpacity = 0.7) %>%
  addMiniMap(position = 'topright',
             width = 100, 
             height = 100,
             toggleDisplay = FALSE) %>%
  addScaleBar(position = "bottomright")
bioclim <- getData(name = "worldclim", res = 2.5, var = "bio", path = "./")

names(bioclim) <- c("Ann Mean Temp","Mean Diurnal Range","Isothermality","Temperature Seasonality",
                    "Max Temp Warmest Mo","Min Temp Coldest Mo","Ann Temp Range","Mean Temp Wettest Qtr",
                    "Mean Temp Driest Qtr","Mean Temp Warmest Qtr","Mean Temp Coldest Qtr","Annual Precip",
                    "Precip Wettest Mo","Precip Driest Mo","Precip Seasonality","Precip Wettest Qtr",
                    "Precip Driest Qtr","Precip Warmest Qtr","Precip Coldest Qtr")

bio_extent <- extent(x = c(
  min(Katy_rgbif_df$x),
  max(Katy_rgbif_df$x),
  min(Katy_rgbif_df$y),
  max(Katy_rgbif_df$y)))

bioclim_extent <- crop(x = bioclim, y = bio_extent)
bioclim_model <- bioclim(x = bioclim_extent, p = cbind(Katy_rgbif_df$x,Katy_rgbif_df$y))
presence_model <- dismo::predict(object = bioclim_model, 
                                 x = bioclim_extent, 
                                 ext = bio_extent)
rastermap<-gplot(presence_model) + 
  geom_polygon(data = us, aes(x= long, y = lat, group = group),
               fill = "gray", color="black") +
  geom_raster(aes(fill=value)) +
  geom_polygon(data = us, aes(x= long, y = lat, group = group),
               fill = NA, color="black") +
  geom_point(data = Katy_rgbif_df, aes(x = x, y = y), size = 2, color = "black", alpha = 0.5) +
  scale_fill_gradientn(colours=c("brown","yellow","darkgreen"), "Probability") +
  coord_fixed(xlim = c(-85,-75), ylim = c(33,37)) +
  xlab("Longitude") + ylab("Latitude") + ggtitle("Probability of ORPU Occurrence") + 
  theme_bw() + theme(plot.title = element_text(hjust = 0.5)) + theme(legend.position = "right") +
  theme(panel.grid.major = element_blank(), 
        panel.grid.minor = element_blank(),
        panel.background = element_rect(fill = "lightblue"))
rastermap

## Rastermap

colors <- c("brown","yellow","darkgreen")

leaflet() %>% 
  addTiles() %>%
  addRasterImage(presence_model, colors = colors, opacity = 0.8) %>%
  addCircleMarkers(Katy_rgbif_df$x,
                   Katy_rgbif_df$y,
                   weight = 1,
                   color = "grey",
                   fillColor = "green",
                   fillOpacity = 0.7) %>%
  addMiniMap(position = 'topright',
             width = 100, 
             height = 100,
             toggleDisplay = FALSE) %>%
  addScaleBar(position = "bottomright")
